Metavariable P:Statement
Metavariable Q:Statement

Rule (BiconditionalImplicationLeftElimination)
  Premises
    P 𝗂𝖿𝖿 Q
    Q
  Conclusion
    P
  Proof
    Q ⇒ P by BiconditionalLeftElimination
  Therefore
    P by ModusPonens

Rule (BiconditionalImplicationRightElimination)
  Premises
    P 𝗂𝖿𝖿 Q
    P
  Conclusion
    Q
  Proof
    P ⇒ Q by BiconditionalRightElimination
  Therefore
    Q by ModusPonens
